ZF Friedrichshafen Plans to Create 5,000 Jobs, Frankfurter Says

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-04-23T09:58:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-23/zf-friedrichshafen-plans-to-create-5-000-jobs-frankfurter-says.html
 Automotive supplier ZF
Friedrichshafen AG plans to create 5,000 jobs by the end of this
year, including 2,000 in  Germany ,  Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung 
said, citing comments by Chief Executive Officer Hans-Georg Haerter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Richard Weiss in Frankfurt at 
